MÔN: TATC
Câu 1. I love French _______ I can't stand Art.
A. or
B. and
C. but
D. because
Đáp án: C. but

Câu 2. I love History _______ I don't like Science.
A. or
B. and
C. but
D. because
Đáp án: C. but

Câu 3. I am _______ rock music. My favorite band is Mayday Parade.
A. into
B. on
C. in
D. over
Đáp án: A. into

Câu 4. _______ Saturday evenings, Sam stays at home with his family.
A. Into
B. In
C. On
D. Over
Đáp án: C. On

Câu 5. I think you should go to _______. There're lots of painting and sculptures there.
A. library
B. art gallery
C. hospital
D. stadium
Đáp án: B. art gallery

Câu 6. If you love _______, you can come and meet our kangaroos and koalas in Australia.
A. natures
B. animals
C. flowers
D. sports
Đáp án: B. animals

Câu 7. She is from Turkey, so she is _______.
A. Greek
B. Irish
C. Polish
D. Turkish
Đáp án: D. Turkish

Câu 8. Have you ever visited _______ of Liberty.
A. Cave
B. Square
C. Statue
D. Pyramid
Đáp án: C. Statue

Câu 9. Is the Mississippi river _______ than the Amazon river?
A. most longest
B. longer
C. more longer
D. longest
Đáp án: B. longer

Câu 10. My mum _______ me with my homework.
A. helps sometimes
B. sometimes helps
C. sometimes help
D. help sometimes
Đáp án: B. sometimes helps

Câu 11. My favorite subject is Chemistry because I like _______ experiments.
A. making
B. playing
C. having
D. doing
Đáp án: D. doing

Câu 12. My best friend Jack _______ gymnastics. He's brilliant!
A. does
B. takes
C. has
D. plays
Đáp án: A. does

Câu 13. What time is it now? – It’s 5:30
A. half past five
B. five fifteen
C. a quarter past five
D. five past half
Đáp án: A. half past five

Câu 14. “What time is it now?” – “It’s 6:40.”
A. twenty to seven
B. six fourteen
C. twenty past seven
D. a quarter past six
Đáp án: A. twenty to seven

